<Layout title="Mentorship | Sheehan Lab">
  <main class="mentorship-page">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <h1>Mentoring Philosophy</h1>
        <p>Developing the next generation of scientific leaders through personalized mentorship</p>
        <div class="hero-pattern"></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="wave-divider">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 1440 120" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <path d="M0,64L80,69.3C160,75,320,85,480,80C640,75,800,53,960,48C1120,43,1280,53,1360,58.7L1440,64L1440,0L1360,0C1280,0,1120,0,960,0C800,0,640,0,480,0C320,0,160,0,80,0L0,0Z" fill="currentColor"/>
      </svg>
    </div>

    <section class="content-area">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="content-wrapper">
          <div class="text-content animate-on-scroll">
            <h2>Personal Development & Growth</h2>
            <div class="mission-statement">
              My goal as your mentor is to help you become the type of scientist you want to be, whether it is in industry or academics, 
              basic, translational or clinical, whether you stay in hematology or take the skills you've learned to another discipline.
            </div>
            <div class="feature-box">
              <div class="info-card">
                <div class="info-card-header">
                  <h3>Diverse Experience</h3>
                </div>
                <p>
                  My PhD was in virology, for example; now I study sickle cell disease. While my focus is to guide you in performing independent 
                  research, I seek to contribute to the development of the whole person.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="info-card">
                <div class="info-card-header">
                  <h3>Personalized Approach</h3>
                </div>
                <p>
                  To do that, I need to understand your current intellectual and professional state as well as your future plans. Each person 
                  I mentor is different, and may have different goals, but I will help you develop certain universal skills:
                </p>
                <div class="skills-grid">
                  <div class="skill-item">
                    <span class="skill-number">01</span>
                    <p>How to ask a compelling scientific question</p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="skill-item">
                    <span class="skill-number">02</span>
                    <p>How to design experiments to answer it</p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="skill-item">
                    <span class="skill-number">03</span>
                    <p>How to interpret and present your findings</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="highlight-box">
                You should expect to have other mentors with other strengths, and know I support activities that broaden your personal 
                and professional development. I'm happy to help you network and identify other mentors.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="section-divider"></div>

    <section class="content-area alternate">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="content-wrapper">
          <div class="text-content animate-on-scroll">
            <h2>Lab Mission & Values</h2>
            <div class="feature-box">
              <p>
                <strong>Our Priority:</strong> I will work tirelessly for the good of the lab. The success of every member of our group is my top priority.
              </p>
              <p>
                <strong>Research Impact:</strong> As part of my job as PI, I am expected to write grants and initiate research that will make meaningful 
                contributions to science, the academic community, and to society. You will help me carry out this research, which demands good and ethical 
                scientific methods.
              </p>
              <p>
                <strong>Scientific Excellence:</strong> It is imperative that we carry out good scientific methods and conduct ourselves in an ethical way. 
                Our priorities include:
              </p>
              <ul class="feature-list">
                <li>Publishing in scientific journals</li>
                <li>Presenting our findings at scientific meetings</li>
                <li>Communicating our work's value to the public</li>
                <li>Engaging in outreach and informal science education</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="section-divider"></div>

    <section class="content-area">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="content-wrapper">
          <div class="text-content animate-on-scroll">
            <h2>My Commitments to You</h2>
            <div class="feature-box">
              <div class="commitment-grid">
                <div class="commitment-card">
                  <h3>Advocacy & Support</h3>
                  <p>I will be your advocate. If you have a problem or challenge, come and see me. 
                  I will do my best to listen and identify a path that will assist in resolving or moving forward.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="commitment-card">
                  <h3>Skill Development</h3>
                  <p>I will facilitate your training in complementary skills needed to be a successful scientist, 
                  including oral and written communication skills, grant writing experience, and professionalism.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="commitment-card">
                  <h3>Career Advancement</h3>
                  <p>I will encourage you to apply for awards, fellowships, and similar opportunities, 
                  and work with you to ensure your applications are competitive.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="commitment-card">
                  <h3>Feedback & Growth</h3>
                  <p>I will provide feedback on your written work, with drafts and deadlines needed in a 
                  timely manner (usually a minimum of one week).</p>
                </div>
                <div class="commitment-card">
                  <h3>Professional Development</h3>
                  <p>I will encourage you to attend scientific/professional meetings and will try 
                  to fund such activities.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="commitment-card">
                  <h3>Leadership Support</h3>
                  <p>I will support your leadership and service aspirations with advice, letters of 
                  recommendation, and more as you request.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="section-divider"></div>

    <section class="content-area alternate">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="content-wrapper">
          <div class="text-content animate-on-scroll">
            <h2>What I Expect From You</h2>
            <div class="feature-box">
              <div class="expectations-grid">
                <div class="expectation-item">
                  <div class="expectation-header">
                    <span class="expectation-number">01</span>
                    <h3>Research Excellence</h3>
                  </div>
                  <p>Plan, design, and conduct high quality scientific research</p>
                </div>
                <div class="expectation-item">
                  <div class="expectation-header">
                    <span class="expectation-number">02</span>
                    <h3>Communication</h3>
                  </div>
                  <p>Present and document your scientific findings</p>
                </div>
                <div class="expectation-item">
                  <div class="expectation-header">
                    <span class="expectation-number">03</span>
                    <h3>Continuous Learning</h3>
                  </div>
                  <p>Stay current with the literature and modern methods</p>
                </div>
                <div class="expectation-item">
                  <div class="expectation-header">
                    <span class="expectation-number">04</span>
                    <h3>Professional Ethics</h3>
                  </div>
                  <p>Be honest, ethical, and enthusiastic</p>
                </div>
                <div class="expectation-item">
                  <div class="expectation-header">
                    <span class="expectation-number">05</span>
                    <h3>Engagement</h3>
                  </div>
                  <p>Engage with the research group and campus programs</p>
                </div>
                <div class="expectation-item">
                  <div class="expectation-header">
                    <span class="expectation-number">06</span>
                    <h3>Respect</h3>
                  </div>
                  <p>Respect lab mates, collaborators, and resources</p>
                </div>
                <div class="expectation-item">
                  <div class="expectation-header">
                    <span class="expectation-number">07</span>
                    <h3>Growth</h3>
                  </div>
                  <p>Take advantage of professional development opportunities</p>
                </div>
                <div class="expectation-item">
                  <div class="expectation-header">
                    <span class="expectation-number">08</span>
                    <h3>Dedication</h3>
                  </div>
                  <p>Work hard - don't give up!</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="section-divider"></div>

    <section class="content-area">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="content-wrapper">
          <div class="text-content animate-on-scroll">
            <h2>Long-term Commitment</h2>
            <div class="feature-box">
              <div class="commitment-highlight">
                I am committed to mentoring you, even after you leave my lab.
              </div>
              <p>
                <strong>Ongoing Support:</strong> I am committed to your education and training while you are in my 
                lab and to guiding your career development - to the degree you wish - long after you leave. I will introduce you to those I have 
                historically mentored or continue to mentor, as they may also serve as strong mentors to you moving forward.
              </p>
              <p>
                <strong>Lasting Relationship:</strong> After graduation or departing from the lab, I remain devoted to supporting the continued 
                professional development of all my lab alumni. Like so many relationships forged during a dramatic period of development, the bond 
                between advisor and student is typically a powerful one.
              </p>
              <p class="highlight-text">
                As you continue your career, your accomplishments honor me and enhance the network for all my trainees.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

